claim.claim-text:
A display apparatus comprising:
an image communication camera comprising an image sensor to sense an image signal, installed to be movable up and down at an upper portion of the display apparatus, and protrudes upwardly from the display apparatus when in use;
an image processor to process the image signal sensed by the image sensor;
a display to display the processed image signal;
a sensor to sense whether the image communication camera is moved up or down;
a power supply to supply electric power to the image communication camera; and
a controller to control the power supply to supply electric power to the image communication camera if the sensor senses that the image communication camera is moved up, and to cut off electric power to the image communication camera if the sensor senses that the image communication camera is moved down.

The method according to one of claims 9 to 12, further comprising sensing an image passed through a lens of the image communication camera;

processing an image signal corresponding to the sensed image; and

displaying an image based on the processed image signal.
